  "content": "## Stream 2: Demo Repo (`corvia-workspace`)\n\n### Task 10: Create `corvia-workspace` Repository Structure\n\nScaffold the demo workspace repo at `/root/corvia-workspace`.\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `/root/corvia-workspace/corvia.toml`\n- Create: `/root/corvia-workspace/.gitignore`\n- Create: `/root/corvia-workspace/repos/.gitkeep`\n- Create: `/root/corvia-workspace/README.md`\n\n**Step 1: Create directory structure**\n\n```bash\nmkdir -p /root/corvia-workspace/repos\nmkdir -p /root/corvia-workspace/.corvia\nmkdir -p /root/corvia-workspace/.devcontainer/scripts\ntouch /root/corvia-workspace/repos/.gitkeep\ntouch /root/corvia-workspace/.corvia/.gitkeep\n```\n\n**Step 2: Write corvia.toml**\n\n```toml\n[project]\nname = \"corvia-demo\"\nscope_id = \"corvia\"\n\n[workspace]\nrepos_dir = \"repos\"\n\n[[workspace.repos]]\nname = \"corvia\"\nurl = \"https://github.com/anthropics/corvia\"\nnamespace = \"kernel\"\n\n[[workspace.repos]]\nname = \"corvia-adapter-git\"\nurl = \"https://github.com/anthropics/corvia-adapter-git\"\nnamespace = \"adapter\"\n\n[storage]\nstore_type = \"lite\"\ndata_dir = \".corvia\"\n\n[embedding]\nprovider = \"ollama\"\nmodel = \"nomic-embed-text\"\nurl = \"http://127.0.0.1:11434\"\ndimensions = 768\n\n[server]\nhost = \"127.0.0.1\"\nport = 8020\n```\n\n**Step 3: Write .gitignore**\n\n```",
